    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>

    <h2>General</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>What is Tridify?</strong>
            <p>Tridify is an application that allows you to discover and explore music, search for albums from iTunes, like your favorite albums, and create your personalized favorites list. Additionally, you will soon be able to share profiles with friends and add album reviews.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How can I get started with Tridify?</strong>
            <p>Getting started with Tridify is easy. You just need to create an account or log in if you already have one. Then, you can search for your favorite albums, like them, and add them to your favorites list.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Account and Authentication</h2>
    <ol start="3">
        <li>
            <strong>Do I need an account to use Tridify?</strong>
            <p>Yes, you need to create an account to access all the features of Tridify, such as liking albums and creating your favorites list.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How can I create an account on Tridify?</strong>
            <p>To create an account on Tridify, simply go to the registration page and fill out the registration form with your information.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Music Search and Discovery</h2>
    <ol start="5">
        <li>
            <strong>Where do the albums on Tridify come from?</strong>
            <p>The albums you find on Tridify are sourced from the iTunes database. You can search and explore a wide variety of music albums from all genres.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How can I search for a specific album on Tridify?</strong>
            <p>To search for a specific album, use the search bar on the homepage and enter the album name, artist name, or any other relevant information about the album you are looking for.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Additional Features</h2>
    <ol start="7">
        <li>
            <strong>How can I like an album on Tridify?</strong>
            <p>To like an album, simply click the "Like" button on the album page. This will add the album to your favorites list.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>How can I share profiles with my friends on Tridify?</strong>
            <p>Sharing profiles with your friends on Tridify will be available soon. We are working on this feature and it will be available in a future update.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>

